dataset.name: sal_np
dataset.sql: ${ "select * from sal_np where yearmonth_int between :start and :end" +(emptyparam("userName")==false ? " and user_name like concat(\'%\',:userName,\'%\')" : "") +(emptyparam("deptIds")==false ? " and user_dept_id in (:deptIds)" : "") +(emptyparam("giveMode")==false ? " and user_give_mode=:giveMode" : "") +" order by user_sort" }

dataset.name: other_bonus
dataset.sql: select sal_id,money money_bonus from sal_bonus where t_name='sal_np'

dataset.name: tax_plus
dataset.sql: select sal_np_id,sum(money) money_plus from sal_np_tax where type='加项' group by sal_np_id

dataset.name: tax_subtract
dataset.sql: select sal_np_id,sum(money) money_subtract from sal_np_tax where type='减项' group by sal_np_id
